  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user it would be nice to have a way retrieving the seed even after it was backed up.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: I had two different accounts, because started to use the app quite a while back and one of the recent derivation changes caused a new account to be created. I did back up one of them but wasn't sure I had the right key and there was no way to extract the seed again once it was backed up.\r\n",
