    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I would like to open this issue up again.  The app has advanced settings already and exporting private key is practically supported by every client.  Since the wallet stores the keys in an insecure location on the phone anyway and that the industry prefers hardware wallets (even Status has its Keycard), I think it makes sense to allow this **and** encourage users to rely on hardware wallets for extra security.",
